citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:19pm on
18-Jan-17.
A telephone message was left for the licensee. The mother of the licensee texted me that she was on jury duty and
the licensee was at work until 6pm..
